<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Aventura Espacial - Learning Menu & Quiz</title>
<style>
  :root { --font-main: 'Poppins', system-ui, sans-serif; }

  body {
